Document: ## Kebabs and Tacos -Meat Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 3 Raw Cutlets for 5 seconds -Hawaiian Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 1 Chili + 1 Raw Cutlet + 1 Pineapple Slice for 5 seconds -Fiesta Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 1 Chili + 1 Corn + 1 Raw Cutlet + Tomato for 5 seconds -Rat Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 1 Raw Rat meat for 10 seconds -Double Rat Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 2 Raw Rat meat for 20 seconds -Human Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 1 Human Torso for 15 seconds -Lizard Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 1 Raw Lizard Meat for 15 seconds -Snake Kebab = Microwave 1 Skewer + 1 Raw Snake Meat + 5u Wine for 15 seconds -Taco Shell = Microwave 1 Flat Tortilla Dough for 5 seconds -Soft Taco = Microwave 1 Dough Slice + 1 Tomato + 2 Onion Slices + 1 Cheese Wedge + 1 Raw Cutlet for 10 seconds -Beef Taco = Microwave 1 Taco Shell + 1 Raw Cutlet + 1 Cheese Wedge for 10 seconds -Beef Taco Supreme = Microwave 1 Taco Shell + 1 Cheese Wedge + 1 Raw Cutlet + 1 Tomato + 1 Cabbage + 2 Onion Slices for 10 seconds -Chicken Taco = Microwave 1 Taco Shell + Raw Chicken Cutlet +1 Cheese Wedge for 10 seconds -Chicken Taco Supreme = Microwave 1 Taco Shell + 1 Cheese Wedge + 1 Raw Chicken Cutlet + 1 Tomato + 1 Cabbage + 2 Onion Slices for 10 seconds -Fish Taco = Microwave 1 Taco Shell + 1 Raw Carp Fillet + 2 Onion Slices + 1 Tomato + 1 Cabbage for 10 seconds -Rat Taco = Microwave 1 Taco Shell + 1 Cheese Wedge + 1 Raw Rat Meat for 10 seconds
